                  <interp inst="t18240407-54-crimeloc308" type="placeName" value="Long-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18240407-54-crimeloc308" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240407-54-off306 t18240407-54-crimeloc308"></join>. A woman told me my handkerchief was gone, and pointed the prisoner out. He ran down, Charterhouse-square, and seeing me close at his heels, threw the handkerchief over into the area of a house in Charterhouse-lane. I caught hold of him, and on returning, the servant of the house gave it to me. I had not felt it taken.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
